description: Teenagers wounded by gunfire overnight in Marion County
story_text:
Two teens shot in Ocala Two teens shot in Ocala. Teenagers wounded by gunfire overnight in Marion County. . Updated: 3:26 AM EDT Jun 11, 2021
				. . . . . . Two teenagers have suffered gunshot wounds overnight in West Ocala, according to the Ocala Police Department.  WESH 2 News is following this breaking news from Marion County where the teens, a boy and a girl, are expected to survive.  According to authorities, the shootings happened around midnight at the Parkside Garden Apartments along Northwest 2nd Street, just east of Interstate 75, north of Silver Springs Boulevard. At this time WESH 2 News has not received any information about a possible suspect.WESH 2 News Sunrise will be following this story, and as more information is known, we will continue to update details.
